,12085,Ctrl+Shift+Click behaves as Ctrl+Click for selection,FileZilla Client,,Bug report,,new,2020-01-07T16:47:17+01:00,2020-01-07T16:47:17+01:00,"Steps to reproduce:
- connect to a server
