,12524,"Colon in filenames on server incorrectly translated to underscore resulting in ""No such file or directory"" error - Windows Devices",FileZilla Client,,Bug report,,reopened,2021-09-05T23:36:38+02:00,2023-04-24T22:16:49+02:00,"When attempting to download files over FTP using the queue the download fails with the error ""''No such file or directory''"".

