,9921,false handling of file attributes in sftp protocol,FileZilla Client,,Bug report,,new,2014-11-24T14:31:15+01:00,2017-08-09T17:24:26+02:00,"filezilla apparently handels file attributes in the sftp protocol by parsing the ""longname"" of the SSH_FXP_NAME resoponse packet. since the format of the longname in sftp version 3 is not 
