furthermore filezilla parses the longname in a false way. Symbolic links  have in the longname the letter ""l"" on the first position instead of ""-"" for files or ""d"" for directories. but filezilla shows symbolic links always as directories regardless of the target it links to, which is wrong.",jimmyjjames
