,10695,"in Site Manager, can't search for site beginning with repeated letter",FileZilla Client,,Bug report,,reopened,2015-11-11T02:23:08+01:00,2015-11-12T13:52:41+01:00,"on Linux (at least) when FileZilla is compiled against GTK3 (at least), searching the sites listed in Site Manager by typing the beginning of the site name does not work if the site name begins with a repeated letter. (presumably this affects repeated letters mid-string, too.)

