,4166,Filezilla isn't a file management tool,FileZilla Client,,Feature request,,reopened,2009-01-15T14:13:27+01:00,2014-02-15T07:19:56+01:00,"This bug report is (in some way) based on tickets submitted before, e.g.: #1345, #2929, #3742, #3746

